OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with spells of cloudy
OL,6,Fweather interspersed with periods of
OL,7,Fsunshine, these most prolonged during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Feeling warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine, though increasingly breezy
OL,10,Fwith an easterly wind developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry overnight with variable
OL,13,Famounts of cloud, strong and gusty
OL,14,Fwinds persisting, particularly across
OL,15,Fthe high ground. Chilly with a touch
OL,16,Fof frost possible in some sheltered
OL,17,Frural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
