OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA chilly start on Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith any cloud soon lifting to leave a
OL,7,Fsunny day with plenty of strong April
OL,8,Fsunshine. Warmer than recent days,
OL,9,Fdespite the windy conditions.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,12,FThursday and Friday with high pressure
OL,13,Fdominating. Often sunny and warm by
OL,14,Fday. Chilly nights with rural frosts
OL,15,Fpossible. Cloudier on Saturday with a
OL,16,Fchance of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
